---
title: Sheet Pan Cheesy Italian Chicken plus Roasted Broccoli, Charred Lemon & Garlic Bread
description: Weeknights feeling busier and more jam-packed than ever? We hear you! That’s why we’re bringing you our quickest, easiest meals yet. Introducing Oven-Ready Dinners. All you have to do is assemble it all on a baking sheet, pop it in the oven, and dig in! No need to worry about prep or dirtying multiple dishes. This week, we’re featuring cheesy herbed chicken, broccoli, garlic bread, and charred lemon for squeezing over everything. It’s all ready in 20 minutes or less—now that’s a weeknight win.
